   If you didn't enjoy MUI-Builder enough to send me some money, please
send me a postcard, a letter, an email to encourage me, give me some
ideas or remarks ... and so on ...  Some people sent me some programs
they made : what an excellent idea !! It seems to me it is one of the
best gifts you can send to me ! If you use MUIBuilder, i would be
