@NODE REQUIRED "Requirements"

	@{b}The requirements for MUI-IControl@{ub}

* Workbench 3.0 (Only tested it with 3.1)
* Mui 3.x (Get it from aminet)

Following libs were used :

* intuition.library v39
* locale.library v38
* muimaster.library v11
* dos.library v39
* iffparse v39
* asl.library v37
* icon.library v37
* screennotify.library v1.0 (optional)

All are standard 3.x libs except for muimaster.library


@ENDNODE

